race.description: Corporate Race Day 11 Feb 2026 F&M Hcp
race.comment: MADAME FIOCCA (12) was second-up from a 22-month spell when successful last time out over 1100m at Goulburn, coming with a well-timed run to get the prize. Takes on a better field here but she has loads of upside and looks up to the task. TRAFALGAR SQUARE (6) is back sharply in distance after a disappointing effort over the Randwick mile recently. Has a terrible win strike rate but has placed three from three at Gosford - each-way claims. NULLARBOR JANE (7) has been very good in her two runs this prep. Up 200m in trip and carries a lot more weight today but cannot be dismissed in this sort of form. The promising ATTRACTIVENESS (9) is in the mix after a comfortable maiden win here last start. CORDINA (14) wasn't all that far away at Canterbury last start and should be peaking after three runs back from a spell.
